Vintage style illustration of a crumbling ancient Roman temple with classical columns, where one massive column bears the unmistakable orange-red hue of Oracle's brand colors, crushing and fragmenting a golden sun-shaped ornate structure beneath it. Scattered across the temple floor are broken ceramic tablets and scrolls, their contents spilling out like lost knowledge. In the background, a determined figure in period-appropriate robes carefully gathers fragments and pieces, placing them into their own personal archive chest for safekeeping. The scene is rendered in warm sepia tones with aged paper texture, evoking vintage technical manuals and old engineering blueprints, with dramatic shadows cast by the setting sun streaming through broken archways.
